   GMap.NET.MapProviders.GoogleMapProvider.Instance.APIKey = GAPIKEY
   GMap.NET.MapProviders.GoogleHybridMapProvider.Instance.APIKey = GAPIKEY
   GMap.NET.MapProviders.GoogleSatelliteMapProvider.Instance.APIKey = GAPIKEY

320 7.027774 192.168.111.111 173.194.35.37 HTTP 337 GET /maps/geo?q=Via+Garibaldi+10+04012+CISTERNA+DI+LATINA+ITALIA+&hl=it&output=csv&key=MYKEY HTTP/1.1 

Where MYKEY is my right google api key.

Anyway I cannot see statistics in my google account

 

Moreover if I set a wrong api key "wrongapikey" all the functions work fine and with wireshark I see
